list.name: Default
list.comment: - Fix Favorites bug and some GUI adjustments.

task.summary: Password help, Cancel membership, Donate us, ... everything related to 'POST' all done. About Us and All Poscasts are half done. From this point onward, the fun begins.
All done, only fast forward feature left.
Adding rotation support for tablet devices
Fix fonts, layout for tablet version. The blue info box is now functional. Media player can now play while rotate, meaning it won't have to reload every time the phone rotates.

Dialogs now retain after orientation. But the termination of asynctasks every time the screen rotates causes NullPointerException to be thrown. To-do: Move all tasks from Asyntasks to the background services.
Finish centralizing codes. Replace all Asycntasks with background services. Rotation is finally conquered. This is the end.

Remove x2 button and center the other 2 buttons. Fix add to favorites behavior. My favorites now displays broadcasts grouped by channels. To-dos: 1. Play broadcast when the app is in the background. Provides user interaction with the app through navigation bar when the app is playing in the background. 2. Keep the phone waking when the broadcast is playing.
Broadcast player can now interact with user via notification bar drawer. Broadcasts in 'My Favorites' are now sorted by Published Date. And tons of other bug fixes and adjustments.
- Fix Favorites bug and some GUI adjustments.
